data.description: Make this ideally situated gem your base camp for all your Vail adventures. This single level, two-bedroom home is located in the popular Sandstone neighborhood—minutes from Vail Village and Lionshead Village, popular hiking/biking trails, golf, and shopping. Steps from 2 Town of Vail complimentary shuttle stops. Ideal rental property, full- or part-time residence.  This bright and airy two bedroom, currently shown as a one bedroom plus sleeping den/office space, looks down on the newly renovated pool and up to Vail Mountain ski run views and holiday fireworks. The home features a private balcony and high-quality finishes - from solid-wood knotty alder doors, Karastan carpet, tumbled marble, and in-unit LG washer/dryer to top-of line stainless steel KitchenAid appliances and hand-hewn barnwood mantel.  It's just a perfect mountain getaway. Relax by the glow of your wood-burning fireplace, enjoy Vail mountain views with your morning coffee and afternoon cocktails, prepare a gourmet meal in your beautiful kitchen and eat at the bar or the intimate dining area. HOA fees include heat!
